prompts.prompt: Create a React component for a SaaS pricing page with multiple plans. Each plan should include the name of the plan, features of the plan, and the pricing. Represent each plan in a card UI element. Also, add a signup button with each plan. Use Tailwind CSS for styling the component. Pass all data via props into the component. Include the component in the index page and use an example of an app hosting SaaS company.
